Title: Why is entropix important? - Tim Kellogg
Kyle Benzle
Description:
While training AI models requires immense GPU power, running
                  those models after they’ve been trained doesn’t. Many
                  companies that once had GPUs on backorder are now realizing
                  that they don’t need as much GPU power as they initially
                  thought. Even a modern MacBook or desktop CPU can run AI
                  models efficiently.
